text.section:
This section does not apply to property:
Leased for business, commercial, manufacturing, mercantile, or industrial purposes, or any other purpose that is not primarily residential;
Improved or to be improved by any apartment, condominium, cooperative, or other building for multifamily use of greater than four dwelling units;
Leased for dwellings or mobile homes that are erected or placed in a mobile home development or mobile home park; or
Subject to an affordable housing land trust agreement executed under Title 14, Subtitle 5 of this article.
